title: Essential Living Foods
description: This is the warehouse and office of the company, but there is a small showroom attached with stock for sale. Everything is raw and many organic and fair trade. Products for sale in the showroom include various nuts, hemp protein, raw cacao butter, raw cacao nibs, goji berries, organic Peruvian olives, coconut oil, coconut sugar, olive oil, dehydrated kale chips, and some other food stuff. Call ahead before you go as their meetings may cause the showroom to close to the public. Previously located on Colorado Ave, Santa Monica.
